Class AbstractGameState

  • java.lang.Object

    AINode, scotlandyard.ScotlandYardView
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DetectiveAIGameState, MyAIGameState

    public abstract class AbstractGameState
extends solution.ScotlandYardModel
implements AINode
    An AbstractGameState is a representation of the state of the game that implements AINode and all of the node related methods e.g score()
